Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出外面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说…这里果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还身处迷宫之中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2}Dungeon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫不知道不知道 渣渣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你的错好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然害我被那种平民所欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-1}窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你的错啊! 窝囊废!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:28.61,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(524,471)\pos(1037,130)\blur2}创世魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杳无人烟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里究竟是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2}Necropolis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前从乌戈君那里听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「牢固的房间」的外面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延伸着遍地死者的街市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概说的就是这样的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「牢固的房间」？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那巨人会说话的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说现在只能召唤出身体部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但确确实实有脑袋的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还很帅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 毕竟是你引以为豪的朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等夺回笛子之后 介绍乌戈君给我认识认识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后关于你的事 我也想更多更多的了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是终点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想要到达的迷宫终点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过分 这个人的前面都被烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这刺伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉丁！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么跟什么啊 开什么狗屁玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渣渣们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贱民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不看看自己是身份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里 根本没有平民和领主之分吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没分别？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是一只既弱又没品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更没生存价值的垃圾渣渣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉丁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像还没有给予你惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩罚！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怪物究竟是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要老子遭那种罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你相当心灵受创啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今发什么牢骚也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是迷宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与地位 血缘 名誉无关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个谁都可以赌上性命并为之奋斗的地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕的话就给我回家找妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥哟~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来对于你这种贱民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要拿出真本领来教训教训不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可知道我学习剑术多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是只有王族才能学到的王宫剑术哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我慢慢折磨死你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这招又如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这点小伎俩么 领主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么砍不中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你满身破绽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满身破绽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师没教过你么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挂科啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是对剑术一知半解的程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高贵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王宫剑术！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会认识托兰语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就决定了与「过去」一刀两断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果身体还是不由自主的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩儿迦娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上来救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能从那么远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬就从这么远的距离！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死心没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要听从这家伙的话到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是迷宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你想要从领主大人身边逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会有人去惩罚你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由 触手可得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩儿迦娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是我最爱的奴隶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死贱民 死贱民！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你会用剑 也是被使役的存在啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有弄懂奴隶的意味嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就让你瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶的正确使用方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我的命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做得到吧 摩儿迦娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我干掉他！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况 你做什么手脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里巴巴君 还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点 那女人不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把笛子还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是抱歉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果我不这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会一直偏袒着那边那个杂鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把笛子还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来强行夺取如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如同老师说过的一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才是引导王的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大的创世魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MAGI！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷 在我离去后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷宫将会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而十年后 某位少年会出现在你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是老师口中所预言的我的力量吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MAGI哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快选我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩儿迦娜她可是那个「法那利斯」的后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的脚力如同天雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连百兽之王狮子的肚子也能一击击穿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是地上最强的猛兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择吧 MAGI哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不想变成可怜的狮子一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就臣服于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把笛子还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会让我成为王的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等这一天很久了 被你选中的这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 我选贤任能 颁布法令 振兴商业 让支乡发展繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 我很厉害 我很伟大 我是能干的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让我成为王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王？ 虽然不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不认为大哥哥你是那样厉害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 阿里巴巴君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法吗 你到底是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人？ 阿里巴巴君 我是你的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 继续冒险吧 向着终点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁要成为王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的算什么啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少喋喋不休了 话都听不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀这不是MAGI吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低下头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 您是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能正常交流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 大概的情况我已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾名为亚蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从礼节和严格创造出来的掌管火焰的神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为这个迷宫的主人 我承认你们攻略该迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻 攻略了 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 亚蒙 我是阿拉丁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是初次见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但是我知道你 MAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MAGI是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MAGI是王的选定者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古往今来 王都是由魔法师挑选出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人的地方 就需要有正确引导他们的王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们便是拥有「王的资质」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而寻找 发掘 引导并锻炼那些王的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是吾等伟大之王所派遣的贤者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的所罗门的化身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正是您啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 攻略了迷宫 就是说这里的东西全部拿走也可以吧 呐~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么选择了那种小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 呐 请你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化身是什么 我到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么人正打算封闭道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话就回不去外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行 让我们回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别瞎囔囔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回去的人进这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个迷宫就要倒塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在这里只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你不回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必要关心那种家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来受尽那家伙折磨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥尔塔斯 你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人 不能让他出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听从这个笨蛋领主的命令 杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不该出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还能回头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到你自己的国家吧 摩儿迦娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我最后的夙愿！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始传送了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥尔塔斯 多尔基斯 都是好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你们想要多少玉米就奖赏你们多少！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勒？摩儿迦娜哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是从所罗门王处所得到的最后的魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样没问题吗 MAGI大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是又被什么奇怪的家伙攻略了 麻烦的又是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你所培养的领主也已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻略了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的冒险旅程也该要完结了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划用这些财宝做本钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在辛德利亚兴创事业
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前给你看过那绘卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个辛巴德所建立的国家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在辛德利亚完成我的辛巴德式的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起的梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 但在那之前要去巴尔巴德这个国家那解决点要事就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒没有什么要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是隐隐感觉到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没遇到你 我这一生都不可能攻略迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是连攻略也不敢提吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到关键时刻便畏缩不前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此而遇到过不可挽回的大失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也可以说我卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太妄自菲薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是有勇气的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得那次沙漠商队的商旅么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你的梦想和名誉被怎样地贬低
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不曾发怒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他人的生存价值被否定的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大发雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视个人安危为鸿毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呐 从那个时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就喜欢上你这个人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 你并不是什么卑鄙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个有勇气的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是我所尊敬的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么冒险旅程结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上还有很多很多值得高兴和兴奋的事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅程还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们全都去游一遍吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的对吧 阿拉丁！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！就这样决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好期待呢 一起去吧！阿里巴巴君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定好了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…郊外的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那小子攻略了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从迷宫的遗迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同传说一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成是那家伙！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很快也会过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好等着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉丁！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒来了么 精灵的孩子哟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.48,0:24:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆 你知道我究竟为何人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 草原牧民
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.81,0:24:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉丁 你去哪儿了
Comment: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:55.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,======OP======
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:59.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,对憧憬的事物 现在 已紧紧地抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:01.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,如同呼啸而出的弹儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,正中心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:09.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}来吧 展翅翱翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:15.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,明天开始才脱胎换骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:17.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,还是对谁不抱希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:22.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,或是这个小道的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还任它们继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:28.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,磨平了棱角的原石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:32.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是 谁都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:37.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思议的 在门的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:43.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,没有V字加身的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:48.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,任谁 在痛苦的尽头 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:54.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,对憧憬的事物 现在 紧紧地抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:59.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,将此身托付于你 将舵交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:04.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,数三声 the show time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:08.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,如同呼啸而出的弹儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,正中心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:16.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}来吧 展翅翱翔吧
Comment: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.71,OP,,0,0,0,,======ED======
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:47.37,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,从单筒望远镜中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:51.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}轻轻的窥望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:02.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,眼中看见的世界  全是往昔的物语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:07.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,为了留住美好的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.58,0:23:13.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有更多的梦想与希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:18.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,若是傻傻发呆  将会使它们白白流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:23.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,与其寻找做不到的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:28.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如着手一试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:31.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,从单筒望远镜中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:33.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻的窥望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:39.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,两手交握  双目相对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:44.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想像吧  要寻找的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:50.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,在脑子里的冒险故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:52.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,单筒望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.87,0:23:55.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,将指往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:24:00.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,透过指间缝隙  能望见什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:05.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,看似远在天边  实则近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:09.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,620)}那如同预言中的宝物
